[thinking] **Evaluating Groovy and Native Image Compatibility**
[thinking] 
[thinking] I'm considering the compatibility of Groovy with Native Image. It seems that while Groovy compiles inline scripts at runtime, Native Image might struggle with that—especially since it can't define classes at runtime with JIT enabled. I wonder if the metadata from org.groovy supports this somehow? It appears that the Groovy runtime isn't very friendly towards Native Image, yet somehow these tests are still building natively. That's definitely worth exploring further!
